    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and usage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it is approaching a service interval where items like brake pads and tires may soon need attention. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind some aesthetic imperfections.",
      "price": 21000.0,
